21 NEW SECTION. Section 8. Internet protocol-enabled service not regulated. (1) An internet
22 protocol-enabled service is not subject to regulation under this title.
23 (2) Except as provided in subsections (3) and (4), an agency, commission, or political subdivision
24 may not enact, adopt, or enforce a law, rule, regulation, ordinance, standard, order, or other provision that
25 regulates the entry, rates, terms, or conditions of any internet protocol-enabled service or otherwise treats
26 providers of internet protocol-enabled service as carriers.
